OL,3,CNottingham Forest v Aston Villa: What
OL,4,Cto expect from the European semi-final
OL,6,FThe Nottingham Forest v Aston Villa
OL,7,FEuropa League semi-final is a huge
OL,8,Fmoment for Midlands football. For the
OL,9,Ffirst time in 44 years we are
OL,10,Fguaranteed a team in a European final.
OL,12,FI visited both clubs ahead of the
OL,13,Ffirst leg and there is a similar
OL,14,Fmessage: Enjoy it.
OL,16,FThere was a brief period when these
OL,17,Ftwo clubs dominated continental
OL,18,Ffootball. Forest were crowned European
OL,19,FChampions in 1979 and 1980; Villa won
OL,20,Fin 1982.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
