OL,3,CNottingham Forest v Aston Villa: What
OL,4,Cto expect from the European semi-final
OL,6,FBut since then both clubs have been
OL,7,Fthrough difficult periods. Just seven
OL,8,Fyears ago this was a regular fixture
OL,9,Fin the second tier Championship.
OL,11,FFor much of this season Forest were on
OL,12,Ftrack for a return there but are now
OL,13,Fin fine form and moving away from
OL,14,Frelegation. It means they can properly
OL,15,Ffocus on this tie.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
