OL,3,CNottingham Forest v Aston Villa: What
OL,4,Cto expect from the European semi-final
OL,6,FThey will need to use the City Ground
OL,7,Fto their advantage tonight. UEFA rules
OL,8,Ffor away fans is different from the
OL,9,FPremier League and so Villa will have
OL,10,Ffewer travelling fans than they did
OL,11,Fjust a few weeks ago in the league.
OL,13,FThe benefit to Villa is they have the
OL,14,Fsecond leg at home, meaning the
OL,15,Fadvantage will switch in their favour
OL,16,Fnext Thursday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
