OL,3,CNottingham Forest v Aston Villa: What
OL,4,Cto expect from the European semi-final
OL,6,FWe saw one of the greatest games in
OL,7,FEuropean history earlier this week as
OL,8,FPSG beat Bayern Munich 5-4 in the
OL,9,FChampions League. No one is expecting
OL,10,Fthat but this is a chance to get the
OL,11,Fworld talking about our football. May
OL,12,Fthe best team in the Midlands win.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
